Usage: verifyTieCell [-help] [-noTieCell <string>] [-powerDomain <string>]
                     [-report <string>]

-help                             # Prints out the command usage
-noTieCell <string>               # Specifies the file name including inst/pin
                                  # name for no tie cell connection check
                                  # (string, optional)
-powerDomain <string>             # Specifies the powerDomain name to check
                                  # (string, optional)
-report <string>                  # Specifies the report file for verifyTieCell
                                  # violations data (string, optional)